ğŸ¯ Guess the Number Game ğŸ®
Guess the Number is a fun and interactive console-based game developed in Java. The game challenges players to guess a randomly selected number between 1 and 100 within a specified number of attempts. With customizable difficulty and user-friendly features, it's a perfect way to sharpen your logical thinking and have some fun!

ğŸ“œ Features
1. Customizable Attempts: Players can choose the number of attempts (between 1 and 6) they want to challenge themselves with.
2. Randomized Gameplay: A new secret number is generated every time you play, ensuring endless fun.
3. User-Friendly Hints: Get instant feedback on whether your guess is too high or too low.
4. Victory and Defeat Messages: Celebrate your win or learn the secret number if you run out of attempts.

ğŸ”§ How to Play
1. Clone or download the repository.
2. Compile and run the program using a Java compiler.
3. Follow the prompts to:
    Choose your desired number of attempts (1-6).
    Guess the secret number within the allowed attempts.
4. Enjoy the game!

